Weather Icons subset for MMT-WeatherOneTheme (`icons/mm`)

Source repository:
https://github.com/erikflowers/weather-icons

This directory contains SVG files copied from the upstream Weather Icons project
and renamed to OpenWeather-style codes (01d..50n) for theme compatibility.

Upstream licensing (from Weather Icons README):
- Weather Icons licensed under SIL OFL 1.1
  http://scripts.sil.org/OFL
- Code licensed under MIT License
  http://opensource.org/licenses/mit-license.html
- Documentation licensed under CC BY 3.0
  http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0

Only icon SVG assets are included here.
